iving whilst under the influence of alcohol macks family requested leniency for the suspect in a letter to the wood green crown court although this was a tragic event for our family the letter reads we feel the accuseds behavior was neither malicious nor intentional and we have no ill will toward him since we learned of the circumstances of the collision popular cultureedit he was illustrated by cartoonist roz chast in a fourpage color strip aliens ahoy published in duke universitys doubletake magazine winter  issue he appears as a character in william baers book of poetry the unfortunates  he was interviewed for the documentary film about the dalai lama dalai lama renaissance where he spoke about his conversations with the dalai lama about aliens but the interview was not included in the final edit of the film life story rights secured in  by makemagic productions for feature film development referencesedit notesedit  feeney mark september   pulitzer winner is killed in accident the boston globe   mack   cevoli cathy july–august  putting it on the line in nevada nuclear times –   matheson  p   human encounters with aliens  part  abductions and the western paradigm intuition network retrieved september     alien thinking bbc news june   retrieved may     httpwwwcsicoporgspecialarticlesshowklassfilesvolume  danielpsheehancom  daniel p sheehan legal strategist and constitutional attorney wwwdanielpsheehannet retrieved september   check date values in accessdate help  thompson paul b  the rockefeller ufo report or how a millionaire and a socialite new ager are trying to influence world leaders about ufos wwwparascopecom parascope inc retrieved september   check date values in accessdate help  the john mack project a true story makemagic productions  retrieved september     a b blumenthal ralph may   alien nation vanity fair retrieved may     bueche will october   driver in dr john mack accident sentenced ufo updates retrieved september     a b dr john mack in the arts 